  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWEEP is a tactical card game. 1 card = 1 bullet—play all 17 cards to unleash explosive damage by skillfully combining card hands, stickers, and items.<br><br><strong>PS. The game doesn’t follow the standard poker hand rules.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick the cards you want straight from the deck and use your wisdom to create the best combinations.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6ac91dc40020b17a4f7cb3d44c2dc46d.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6ac91dc40020b17a4f7cb3d44c2dc46d.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Transform Cards into Bullets and Trigger Chain Reactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize stickers and items on the cards to trigger an astonishing chain of effects, transforming cards into bullets to unleash devastating damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/3105538dca1bdab6eecae83ca2482a2c.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/3105538dca1bdab6eecae83ca2482a2c.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clear Your Hand, Seize Control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you clear your hand, you gain a brand-new turn and double all damage dealt. Keep clearing cards to overpower your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6bc77450aeacdfc9fffc2a194ff85789.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6bc77450aeacdfc9fffc2a194ff85789.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you stack items for massive damage or masterfully play for extra turns, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWEEP is a tactical card game. 1 card = 1 bullet—play all 17 cards to unleash explosive damage by skillfully combining card hands, stickers, and items.<br><br><strong>PS. The game doesn’t follow the standard poker hand rules.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick the cards you want straight from the deck and use your wisdom to create the best combinations.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6ac91dc40020b17a4f7cb3d44c2dc46d.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6ac91dc40020b17a4f7cb3d44c2dc46d.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Transform Cards into Bullets and Trigger Chain Reactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize stickers and items on the cards to trigger an astonishing chain of effects, transforming cards into bullets to unleash devastating damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/3105538dca1bdab6eecae83ca2482a2c.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/3105538dca1bdab6eecae83ca2482a2c.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clear Your Hand, Seize Control</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you clear your hand, you gain a brand-new turn and double all damage dealt. Keep clearing cards to overpower your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6bc77450aeacdfc9fffc2a194ff85789.poster.avif?t=1755396112\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393180/extras/6bc77450aeacdfc9fffc2a194ff85789.webm?t=1755396112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you stack items for massive damage or masterfully play for extra turns, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
